room_title: Escape room "Mystery In Paris" by Amazing Escape Room in New York
room_address: 585 N. Gannon Ave Staten Island, NY 10314
room_description: Follow the detective back in time to Paris 1927, in this live action murder mystery.  Learn about your character and retrace their steps in a game where everyone is connected, and everyone is a suspect. Keep track of the events, and follow the evidence to identify where the detective was last seen, who he was with and what the suspect had.
